Pre-Game Insights: The Thunder are at the infancy stages of their title window while the Warriors just want to be competitive in Stephen Curry's twilight.
Post-Match Reflections: Jalen Williams — the unofficial ring leader of the tradition — pays no attention to the outside noise, saying 'We enjoy it.'
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Thunder are the first team to start their season 7-0 with all double-digit point margins.
Others: A possible rivalry between the Oklahoma City Thunder and the Golden State Warriors has gained another reason to be must-watch television.
